@NODE HydroZone
@{APEN 3}@{B}HYDROZONE@{UB}@{APEN 1}
~~~~~~~~~~
Fly through fast, speedy 3D tunnels trying not to crash.
Magazine review quotes of HydroZone:- @{I}
"This shareware effort, from little known Skull Army Software, could 
with a lot of polishing pass for a commercial release. As it stands 
at the moment it is far better than average PD games, the first in 
fact to earn our all-new PD games of the month accolade." @{ui}
@{B}Amiga Action (Game of the Month) October 1994 @{UB}



@{APEN 3}@{B}SPEED RACER FX@{UB}@{APEN 1}
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Sequel to HydroZone.  Race against Human or Computer controlled 
players, up to 6 in a league, through super fast 3D tunnels with a 
split screen view.  Plus make your own levels using the supplied 
Tunnel Designer.

This game is the winner of the 'Amiga Formats' magazine best Cover CD 
game, March 1997.
@ENDNODE                              

